UI Design Ideas
- Pages
    - Home
        - Upcoming Tasks
        - Toggle to sort all tasks
        - New Task
        - Streak/Progress Indicator
    - Task Entry Page/Modal
        - Text input box with voice input button
        - All other mentioned task details
        - Confirmation of AI Generated task entry
    - Task Details Page
        - All details about a task
        - Option to edit task
        - Mark as complete or snooze
    - Settings Page
        - Notification Settings
        - Google Calender Integration
        - Language Settings

